{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e012dc5b8c","title":"主要偏向是“冒进”","origin":"中国人民大学经济系政治经济学教研室编《中国资產阶级右派经济言论批判参考资料》，1958年9月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"590ba9d4f3","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"e012dc5b8c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"},{"id":"e930fcdff1","name":"陈丘民"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a29d1fb687","type":"title","text":"主要偏向是“冒进”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"3575e46caf","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学陈丘民","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"7e76b6a101","type":"subtitle","text":"（陈丘民：中国人民大学法律系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"aa7c21ed92","type":"paragraph","text":"关于当前工作中的主要偏向是“保守”还是“冒进”的问题。他认为从1956年以来主要是冒进，而不是保守。这不是那个人的问题，也不是那个部的问题，而是全部的冒进。张奚若先生说的“好大喜功”、“急功近利”，都是说的它的表现。这是把毛主席所说的“稳步前进”忘了的结果。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"a95358e1e8","type":"paragraph","text":"今天的所有制是社会主义的，生产力水平不是社会主义的，人民的精神生活是社会主义的，而物质生活不是社会主义的。中国建设社会主义有冒进。结果：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"79af0f3104","type":"paragraph","text":"a。除主要大城市外，全国中小城市都衰退了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"8125f8be43","type":"paragraph","text":"b。农业生产相对减产了。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"},{"id":"7a6450a6e7","type":"appellation","text":"（摘自“法律系学生陈丘民关于我国国家制度和国际问题的荒谬言论（节录）”，载《社会主义思想教育参考资料选辑》第四辑第236页）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c"}],"page":{"id":"e58f9eeab8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e012dc5b8c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}